			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a85b30acea7f65ad3ea3d0d4a7a853c1?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn">Мила</cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>
		
